Yo Tzu is missing. Traces of blood.
I'm almost certain it's his.

259
00:21:38,666 --> 00:21:41,041
There are surveillance cameras here.

260
00:21:41,125 --> 00:21:42,541
<i>I need your help right now.</i>

261
00:21:48,791 --> 00:21:51,708
Okay. What do you want me to do?

262
00:21:51,791 --> 00:21:54,708
<i>Check on any suspicious person or vehicle.</i>

263
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:58,916
Between 2:00 a.m. and 3:00.

264
00:21:59,708 --> 00:22:03,125
Chengdu Street. Lane 10. Got it?

265
00:22:07,666 --> 00:22:08,666
Yes.

266
00:22:25,875 --> 00:22:28,125
<i>Reversed Obelisk.</i>

267
00:22:28,208 --> 00:22:30,333
<i>Orient Express.</i>

268
00:22:30,416 --> 00:22:32,291
<i>Reversed Amazonia.</i>

269
00:22:33,125 --> 00:22:38,666
<i>In the future,</i>
<i>someone will be stabbed to death.</i>

270
00:22:38,750 --> 00:22:40,875
<i>I'm really sorry.</i>

271
00:23:14,375 --> 00:23:16,166
Help me!

272
00:23:28,458 --> 00:23:30,541
Between 2:30 and 3:00 a.m.,

273
00:23:30,625 --> 00:23:33,750
seven vehicles entered
or exited that lane.

274
00:23:35,500 --> 00:23:37,833
One of those seven
has been reported stolen.

275
00:23:38,458 --> 00:23:40,208
Track that stolen car.

276
00:23:40,791 --> 00:23:42,708
No answer, still.

277
00:23:43,375 --> 00:23:44,500
Keep calling.

278
00:23:46,125 --> 00:23:47,958
<i>I'm in Zhonghua Road.</i>

279
00:23:48,500 --> 00:23:51,041
The car traveled east from there

280
00:23:52,208 --> 00:23:54,125
and took the elevated expressway.

281
00:23:54,750 --> 00:23:57,708
<i>Then it took Civic Boulevard</i>
<i>in the direction of Nangang.</i>

282
00:24:49,041 --> 00:24:51,500
Next turn is Huandong Boulevard.

283
00:24:53,958 --> 00:24:58,500
Oh! Wait. I have its last location
at Unit 20, Qiedong Street, Xizhi.

284
00:24:58,583 --> 00:25:00,541
- <i>I'm close.</i>
- Wait-- No, don't hang up!

285
00:25:00,625 --> 00:25:03,333
- Don't hang up.
- Okay. Send it to me. Now.

286
00:25:04,166 --> 00:25:06,166
I've sent it.

287
00:25:06,250 --> 00:25:09,166
Bye-bye.

288
00:26:51,791 --> 00:26:54,041
Yo Tzu! Yo Tzu!

289
00:27:04,875 --> 00:27:07,333
- Hey, are you sure he's here?
- Shh!

290
00:27:07,958 --> 00:27:09,791
But he's not dead, is he?

291
00:27:09,875 --> 00:27:11,333
What are you doing now?

292
00:27:14,333 --> 00:27:15,375
You hear that?

293
00:27:16,416 --> 00:27:17,916
Yeah. What is that?

294
00:28:11,625 --> 00:28:13,791
<i>Every prediction has the same method.</i>

295
00:28:13,875 --> 00:28:15,666
<i>She is the mastermind…</i>

296
00:28:17,750 --> 00:28:20,500
<i>Then they put a cloth over my mouth…</i>

297
00:28:20,583 --> 00:28:23,083
<i>Then, I woke up in a car trunk…</i>

298
00:28:25,208 --> 00:28:27,166
<i>He was also in that same trunk…</i>

299
00:28:34,958 --> 00:28:38,333
<i>Hi, guys. I'm in hospital right now.</i>

300
00:28:40,041 --> 00:28:42,958
<i>Witch Baba's prediction almost came true.</i>

301
00:28:44,791 --> 00:28:48,166
<i>I'm the one who was stabbed</i>
<i>in Witch Baba's prediction.</i>

302
00:28:50,708 --> 00:28:53,250
Last night, I…

303
00:28:56,375 --> 00:28:57,791
…was in the city…

304
00:29:02,125 --> 00:29:04,333
when someone came up behind me.

305
00:29:06,166 --> 00:29:08,083
Then I felt a sharp pain.

306
00:29:14,666 --> 00:29:16,375
It all happened so quick.

307
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:26,375
Then they put a cloth over my mouth.

308
00:29:27,333 --> 00:29:29,708
It smelled weird, and I couldn't breathe.

309
00:29:33,333 --> 00:29:34,833
I can't remember much.

310
00:29:40,500 --> 00:29:43,000
Then, I woke up in a car trunk…

311
00:29:45,708 --> 00:29:47,500
with blood everywhere.

312
00:29:48,583 --> 00:29:49,916
In the end…

313
00:29:51,958 --> 00:29:53,666
Officer Jen saved me.

314
00:30:04,500 --> 00:30:06,541
In the trunk, I found this.

315
00:30:22,375 --> 00:30:23,916
Wa Zai's earring.

316
00:30:31,541 --> 00:30:36,291
He was… he was also in that same trunk.

317
00:30:47,333 --> 00:30:49,416
<i>Everything makes sense now.</i>

318
00:30:51,375 --> 00:30:55,875
<i>Witch Baba locked me and Wa Zai</i>
<i>in that trunk, waiting for us to die.</i>

319
00:30:55,958 --> 00:31:00,041
<i>And after her predictions spread,</i>
<i>she'd throw out our corpses,</i>

320
00:31:00,125 --> 00:31:03,125
<i>making it look</i>
<i>like her prediction came true.</i>

321
00:31:03,875 --> 00:31:06,208
Every prediction has the same method.

322
00:31:06,291 --> 00:31:08,583
She is the mastermind.

323
00:31:15,458 --> 00:31:17,958
Hello. We're Egg Water River. Boom, boom!

324
00:31:18,041 --> 00:31:21,375
Today, we're talking
about the urban legend Witch Baba.

325
00:31:21,458 --> 00:31:23,250
- Who's gone viral.
- That's right.

326
00:31:23,333 --> 00:31:26,833
The name Witch Baba
came from a psychic from Bulgaria

327
00:31:26,916 --> 00:31:28,166
whose name is Baba Vanga.

328
00:31:28,250 --> 00:31:29,083
Vanga.

329
00:31:29,166 --> 00:31:32,291
The tarot cards she uses
are from a normal card game.

330
00:31:32,375 --> 00:31:34,750
- Just ordinary cards.
- Just normal cards.

331
00:31:34,833 --> 00:31:36,750
You keep acting.

332
00:31:37,750 --> 00:31:38,916
How about you…

333
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:41,250
stop being a little bitch-ass?!

334
00:31:41,333 --> 00:31:45,000
Most fortune-telling relies
on a person's psychological illusions.

335
00:31:45,083 --> 00:31:47,416
- That's right.
- But her method is brutal.

336
00:31:47,500 --> 00:31:50,375
Her predictions rely
on the post hoc fallacy.

337
00:31:50,458 --> 00:31:52,375
Huh? Post hoc fallacy? What?

338
00:31:52,458 --> 00:31:53,916
I'll explain it to you.

339
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:55,166
It's a coincidence!

340
00:31:55,250 --> 00:31:57,125
- What the helly?!
- Yeah. Real talk. Yep.

341
00:31:57,208 --> 00:32:01,791
I think Witch Baba is the mastermind
behind all of these murders.

342
00:32:01,875 --> 00:32:06,416
Wa Zai, Yo Tzu, Lin Po-lun,
and Wei Yen was influenced by Witch Baba.

343
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:08,333
All because of her predictions.

344
00:32:08,416 --> 00:32:11,500
When Wei Yen went
to the police station, he didn't film it.

345
00:32:11,583 --> 00:32:15,500
If he was there to make content,
why didn't he take a camera with him?

346
00:32:17,250 --> 00:32:19,583
Basically, it's a logical error.

347
00:32:19,666 --> 00:32:22,083
Think about it. Yeah,
it's like news about the lotto,

348
00:32:22,166 --> 00:32:24,791
or a traffic accident, or an earthquake.

349
00:32:24,875 --> 00:32:26,333
Something's always happening.

350
00:32:26,416 --> 00:32:28,083
Show me a day with no accident!

351
00:32:28,166 --> 00:32:29,791
Show me a day with no earthquake.

352
00:32:29,875 --> 00:32:31,583
I crush you every three months!

353
00:32:31,666 --> 00:32:35,916
So, Witch Baba's videos
are purely coincidental.

354
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:39,958
This is a joke.
We all know why you wear a mask.

355
00:32:40,708 --> 00:32:41,625
Because…

356
00:32:41,708 --> 00:32:44,000
you're hideously ugly! Disgusting!

357
00:32:44,083 --> 00:32:47,000
- Sometimes, she posts every three days.
- Right.

358
00:32:47,083 --> 00:32:49,666
Sometimes, it's every three months.

359
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:51,291
- What's she waiting for?
- Tell me.

360
00:32:51,375 --> 00:32:53,708
She's waiting for something to happen!

361
00:32:53,791 --> 00:32:58,625
I don't know why she's targeting us.
We're just normal people who make videos.

362
00:32:58,708 --> 00:33:01,625
But nothing will stop us
from being passionate about this.

363
00:33:01,708 --> 00:33:05,666
Only recently did she start
posting more predictions.

364
00:33:05,750 --> 00:33:06,583
Oh.

365
00:33:06,666 --> 00:33:10,875
And Yo Tzu said that she wants
predictions to come true.

366
00:33:10,958 --> 00:33:13,291
So, Witch Baba, I'm warning you.

367
00:33:13,375 --> 00:33:16,333
You better watch out,
or you're gonna be next.

368
00:33:16,416 --> 00:33:18,791
LITTLE EGG ROASTS DUCK EGG

369
00:33:18,875 --> 00:33:23,708
To Witch Baba.
Whoever you are, we will find you.

370
00:33:23,791 --> 00:33:26,041
You also make online videos.

371
00:33:26,916 --> 00:33:30,583
Please turn yourself in
before you hurt anyone else.

372
00:33:30,666 --> 00:33:32,041
Stop killing.

373
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:35,125
GO ON, CONTINUE ACTING

374
00:33:35,208 --> 00:33:37,833
THIS IS AN INFLUENCER'S DAILY LIFE,
NO SURPRISE THERE

375
00:33:37,916 --> 00:33:38,916
CUT THE CRAP

376
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,208
YOU'RE JUST WASTING TIME

377
00:33:59,875 --> 00:34:02,375
Mr. Jen? You were looking for me?

378
00:34:02,458 --> 00:34:04,458
Yeah. I want you to meet someone.

379
00:34:04,541 --> 00:34:05,541
Thank you.

380
00:34:09,500 --> 00:34:10,750
Where are we going?

381
00:34:12,416 --> 00:34:14,500
EMERGENCY

382
00:34:17,583 --> 00:34:19,833
Come in.

383
00:34:21,500 --> 00:34:24,958
Oh! If it isn't my savior.

384
00:34:25,916 --> 00:34:28,041
And you brought me gourmet food.

385
00:34:29,375 --> 00:34:32,208
Ding Shang fried rice. It's delicious.

386
00:34:32,291 --> 00:34:34,125
- Fried rice?
- Yep.

387
00:34:34,208 --> 00:34:35,541
You shouldn't have.

388
00:34:35,625 --> 00:34:39,166
Ah. You're recovering well.
You filming, huh?

389
00:34:40,625 --> 00:34:43,208
If you came a bit later,
you would've missed me.

390
00:34:44,666 --> 00:34:47,333
- I would've missed seeing a loser.
- Huh?

391
00:34:48,291 --> 00:34:49,833
A loser with a million followers.

392
00:34:49,916 --> 00:34:51,958
Who's she?

393
00:34:56,000 --> 00:35:00,666
Hi. I'm Li Hsin-ping from
the High-Tech Crime Investigation Unit.

394
00:35:00,750 --> 00:35:02,708
- Hey.
- I've seen your…

395
00:35:03,583 --> 00:35:05,625
"What's Up Yo! Yo!" channel.

396
00:35:05,708 --> 00:35:07,291
Thank you.

397
00:35:08,250 --> 00:35:09,416
I have a few questions.

398
00:35:09,500 --> 00:35:11,166
I already said everything
in my live stream.

399
00:35:11,250 --> 00:35:13,125
Is this the person who kidnapped you?

400
00:35:13,208 --> 00:35:15,166
- I don't know. I didn't see.
- Look carefully.

401
00:35:18,125 --> 00:35:19,375
I don't know.

402
00:35:22,875 --> 00:35:24,916
Do you know if it was a guy or a girl?

403
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:34,833
It…

404
00:35:36,791 --> 00:35:38,166
wasn't a girl.

405
00:35:39,041 --> 00:35:39,875
Uh…

406
00:35:39,958 --> 00:35:42,333
Are you sure? Think again.

407
00:35:43,333 --> 00:35:45,541
I don't know. I couldn't see anything.

408
00:35:45,625 --> 00:35:48,791
Have you guys offended anyone at any time?

409
00:35:48,875 --> 00:35:50,916
- "You guys"?
- Yes, "you guys."

410
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:54,750
Wa Zai or Wei Yen.
You often film together.

411
00:35:54,833 --> 00:35:58,333
You're brats. Your words
could easily have offended people.

412
00:35:58,416 --> 00:36:00,166
Hey, what is she talking about?

413
00:36:01,541 --> 00:36:05,000
We think this person is targeting you.

414
00:36:05,583 --> 00:36:06,958
How do you know?

415
00:36:07,041 --> 00:36:08,375
That guy last night,

416
00:36:08,458 --> 00:36:11,458
the guy who was stabbed,
he's not connected to us.

417
00:36:12,250 --> 00:36:14,791
- Yeh Pin-hsuan?
- Who's she?

418
00:36:22,166 --> 00:36:23,500
Never met her.

419
00:36:24,583 --> 00:36:27,375
We suspect she killed Lin Po-lun.

420
00:36:27,458 --> 00:36:29,875
But presently, we don't have a motive.

421
00:36:31,208 --> 00:36:35,125
But we're sure
that Wa Zai's killer was male.

422
00:36:35,208 --> 00:36:36,291
Huh?

423
00:36:36,375 --> 00:36:39,958
But she was present at both crime scenes.

424
00:36:40,041 --> 00:36:42,166
And in RS E-Sports.

425
00:36:42,875 --> 00:36:44,958
Post hoc fallacy.

426
00:36:46,541 --> 00:36:49,333
Oh! You watched the video!

427
00:36:49,416 --> 00:36:52,750
Oh. Uh…

428
00:36:54,416 --> 00:36:56,500
Check your phone.

429
00:36:58,708 --> 00:36:59,958
We gotta go.

430
00:37:02,333 --> 00:37:05,041
Hey, wait. What happened?

431
00:37:12,583 --> 00:37:16,291
<i>Witch Baba locked me</i>
<i>and Wa Zai in that trunk, waiting to die.</i>

432
00:37:16,375 --> 00:37:20,208
<i>And after the prediction spreads,</i>
<i>she'd throw out our corpses,</i>

433
00:37:20,291 --> 00:37:23,041
<i>making it look</i>
<i>like her prediction came true.</i>

434
00:37:25,583 --> 00:37:30,041
<i>Every prediction has the same method.</i>
<i>She is the mastermind.</i>

435
00:37:37,250 --> 00:37:38,791
- Witch Baba?
- Huh?

436
00:37:46,625 --> 00:37:48,375
POLICE ANNOUNCE WITCH BABA'S IDENTITY

437
00:37:56,625 --> 00:37:58,583
BREAKING NEWS!
WITCH BABA'S IDENTITY EXPOSED!

438
00:38:01,791 --> 00:38:04,000
IT'S ACTUALLY
AN ONLINE CAKE SHOP'S LADY BOSS!

439
00:38:05,166 --> 00:38:07,583
<i>- Someone found Witch Baba?</i>
<i>- This time, the police confirmed it.</i>

440
00:38:07,666 --> 00:38:09,791
<i>- Dox!</i>
<i>- I found her name.</i>

441
00:38:13,291 --> 00:38:14,291
YEH PIN-HSUAN

442
00:38:16,666 --> 00:38:18,375
<i>- Yeh Pin-hsuan?</i>
<i>- Murderer!</i>

443
00:38:18,458 --> 00:38:20,208
<i>- Dox her.</i>
<i>- Let's make this go viral.</i>

444
00:38:20,291 --> 00:38:22,500
YEH PIN-HSUAN - ABOUT
PRE-ORDER PHONE NUMBER - COPY

445
00:38:25,625 --> 00:38:27,458
<i>- There's even an address.</i>
<i>- How do we know it was her?</i>

446
00:38:27,541 --> 00:38:29,750
<i>- Someone post a photo.</i>
<i>- Let's all organize a rally together.</i>

447
00:38:29,833 --> 00:38:31,708
<i>- She's quite cute.</i>
<i>- She looks prettier with a mask on.</i>

448
00:38:31,791 --> 00:38:33,958
<i>- So this is what a killer looks like.</i>
<i>- It's true this time, right?</i>

449
00:38:34,041 --> 00:38:36,000
<i>- Someone found Witch Baba?</i>
<i>- Yeah, the police confirmed it.</i>

450
00:38:36,083 --> 00:38:37,083
<i>Give back Wa Zai's life.</i>

451
00:38:37,166 --> 00:38:40,291
<i>- She definitely did it. Just look at her.</i>
<i>- We should all meet and confront her.</i>

452
00:38:47,333 --> 00:38:49,791
OCTOBER 5TH

453
00:38:55,916 --> 00:38:59,125
Chia-jen! Chen-wei! Get in here.

454
00:39:09,250 --> 00:39:10,583
It was me.

455
00:39:12,458 --> 00:39:13,458
About this release…

456
00:39:13,541 --> 00:39:17,375
It's my fault, sir. I misspoke,
but I really didn't mean to.

457
00:39:17,458 --> 00:39:18,833
I'm sorry.

458
00:39:20,958 --> 00:39:22,416
Is this your doing?

459
00:39:26,208 --> 00:39:29,875
Chia-jen, I've warned you.
The internet's not that straightforward.

460
00:39:29,958 --> 00:39:31,375
Is this what I wanna hear?!

461
00:39:32,375 --> 00:39:35,000
The netizens are going to solve this
before we do.

462
00:39:36,666 --> 00:39:38,916
Find Yeh Pin-hsuan and fix this!

463
00:39:43,250 --> 00:39:45,625
Also, Chen-wei.

464
00:39:46,208 --> 00:39:49,000
I'm holding your unit responsible
for this too.

465
00:39:49,083 --> 00:39:50,125
Yes, sir.

466
00:40:07,583 --> 00:40:09,416
Now what's going on?!

467
00:40:16,125 --> 00:40:18,416
Witch Baba's uploaded a new vid.

468
00:40:25,416 --> 00:40:27,083
WITCH BABA

469
00:40:27,166 --> 00:40:30,708
<i>Hello, everyone. I'm Witch Baba.</i>

470
00:40:30,791 --> 00:40:33,083
<i>Today is October 5th.</i>

471
00:40:33,625 --> 00:40:37,666
<i>Last time, I predicted</i>
<i>that someone will be stabbed.</i>

472
00:40:37,750 --> 00:40:39,416
<i>And it came true.</i>

473
00:40:39,500 --> 00:40:43,625
<i>Let's see what the tarot cards</i>
<i>have for us today! </i>

474
00:40:45,416 --> 00:40:47,708
<i>Upright Weather Radar.</i>

475
00:40:50,458 --> 00:40:53,541
<i>Reversed London Big Ben.</i>

476
00:40:54,916 --> 00:40:56,708
<i>Reversed Alien.</i>

477
00:40:58,291 --> 00:40:59,875
<i>In the future,</i>

478
00:40:59,958 --> 00:41:03,666
<i>someone will fall to their death</i>
<i>from a bridge.</i>
